{"tid":766494,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（月經）幾個好鍾意嘅香港配音員","createTime":"2018-08-03T15:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T11:18:03.000Z","uid":176960,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"31b3df4ba52de5650b8c5a49bb1ba5ee96cad7af","tid":766494,"uid":176960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"細細個睇TVB大，有幾個人把聲我好鍾意，<br />\n唔知大家有無同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陳欣<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WwfqaKwu_gY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWwfqaKwu_gY&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b0048b52\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WwfqaKwu_gY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n代表作<br />\n柏木達也《同一屋簷下》<br />\n旁白《櫻桃小丸子》<br />\n藏馬《幽遊白書》<br />\n毛利小五郎《名偵探柯南》<br />\n里昂李奧《全職獵人》<br />\n黑傑克《怪醫黑傑克》<br />\n閔政浩《大長今》<br />\n侯國基《醫神》系列<br />\n錫巴斯查恩&middot;米加艾里斯<br />\n 《黑執事》<br />\nAll Might《我的英雄學院》<br />\n劉在錫《Running Man》<br />\n夏洛克&middot;福爾摩斯<br />\n 《福爾摩斯新傳》系列<br />\n金魔君《魔鬼神探》系列<br />\n<br />\n最鍾意佢配Hunter嘅里昂李奧，完全勁match,<br />\n直頭覺得好似佢本人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沈小蘭<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h0QdbU2GZ5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh0QdbU2GZ5w&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=32fef669\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h0QdbU2GZ5w</a>（46秒開始）<br />\n<br />\n代表作<br />\n星仔《星仔走天涯》<br />\n阿丁《神勇飛鷹俠》系列<br />\n一休《機靈小和尚》<br />\n剛田太太《叮噹／哆啦A夢》<br />\n大道寺知世《百變小櫻Magic咭》<br />\n火渡凱《爆旋陀螺》<br />\n塔矢亮《棋靈王》<br />\n北島真夜《玻璃面具》<br />\n土萌螢《美少女戰士》<br />\n施蓮妮《靚太唔易做》系列<br />\n榮安慈《24》系列<br />\n唐愛暉《F檔案》系列<br />\n<br />\n以前仲有一套卡通，個樣好似一隻長頸鹿嘅，<br />\n印象中果把聲好可愛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘇強文<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7sOg4kT8YQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7sOg4kT8YQk&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=24bf181d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7sOg4kT8YQk</a><br />\n<br />\n代表作<br />\n杜拉格斯《龍珠二世》<br />\n嘉美尤&middot;維達《機動戰士再起風雲》<br />\n展昭《包青天》系列<br />\n瀨名秀俊《悠長假期》<br />\n藤原佐為《棋靈王》<br />\n高嶺清麻呂《魔法小神童加旋》<br />\n楊過《神鵰俠侶》<br />\n蛭魔妖一《衝鋒21》<br />\n莫霍斯《X檔案》系列<br />\n鄺路加《仁心仁術》系列<br />\n施米高《逃》系列<br />\n賀正《欲骨查》系列<br />\n<br />\n由細到大都覺得佢把聲好斯文&amp;溫柔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林元春<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0W8kGLbt2aM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0W8kGLbt2aM&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=95e80578\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0W8kGLbt2aM</a><br />\n<br />\n代表作<br />\n音無響子《相聚一刻》<br />\n孫悟飯（童年）《龍珠二世》<br />\n豆釘兔《美少女戰士R》<br />\n木之本櫻《百變小櫻Magic咭》<br />\n穗波小玉《櫻桃小丸子》<br />\n叮鈴／多啦美《叮噹／哆啦A夢》<br />\n佳娜德《寶石寵物》<br />\n八神光《數碼暴龍》<br />\n藤原初貴《小魔女Doremi》<br />\nTamama《Keroro軍曹》<br />\n花帶柑《我們這一家》<br />\n朝比奈實玖瑠《涼宮春日的憂鬱》<br />\n中野梓《K-ON! 輕音少女》<br />\n梅艾比《史前逃龍》系列<br />\n簡美琪《行屍》系列<br />\n<br />\n基本上我覺得佢把聲完全係carry到任何妹妹角色，<br />\n尤其是小櫻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁偉德<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yFCOg8Gkfls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyFCOg8Gkfls&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=96a4eb19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yFCOg8Gkfls</a><br />\n<br />\n代表作<br />\n希羅&middot;尤《新機動戰記》<br />\n喵喵怪《神奇寶貝》系列<br />\n月城雪兔（審判者月）<br />\n 《百變小櫻Magic咭》<br />\n名古屋稚空（怪盜辛巴達）<br />\n 《神風怪盜》<br />\n基拉&middot;大和《機動戰士特種計劃》<br />\n夜神月《死亡筆記》<br />\nDororo《Keroro軍曹》<br />\n桂小太郎《銀魂》<br />\n鮑七里（鮑阿七）《特務阿七》系列<br />\n李光洙《Running Man》<br />\n<br />\n喵喵怪，夜神月，基拉大和⋯⋯不解釋<br />\n童年基本上都係聽佢大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭志權<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6t3X_gVQxr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6t3X_gVQxr0&d=q4FXmBfltMjuU5BmqwIVUsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c6d82b88\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6t3X_gVQxr0</a><br />\n<br />\n代表作<br />\n柏木雅也《同一屋簷下》<br />\n比達《龍珠二世》<br />\n浦飯幽助《幽遊白書》<br />\n花輪和彥《櫻桃小丸子》<br />\n金田一一《金田一之少年事件簿》<br />\n旁白《西遊記》<br />\n<br />\n細細個聽到西遊記佢把聲就覺得好正，<br />\n但可惜聽得唔耐佢就離開TVB"},{"pid":"d2b25010647659f2287110b8cf1e567c012a3e8e","tid":766494,"uid":194071,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"林保全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216d027de4cf66a5bffb00fcbe959bac00f8fa23","tid":766494,"uid":176960,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d2b25010647659f2287110b8cf1e567c012a3e8e","tid":766494,"uid":194071,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"林保全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"雖則保全叔嘅多啦A夢好經典，<br />\n但我細個唔太鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80819f5c894ff45db5853deab6692edf537eef7a","tid":766494,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"陳欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配中佬好有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878e8f65f28ea49dc53a825e458088ec95c3a266","tid":766494,"uid":60709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"林元春<br />\n何璐怡"},{"pid":"1f930e25744df85aa71f69626a4e973a6ac53e32","tid":766494,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"現代配音員我超鍾意李凱傑<br />\n把聲好好丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2343d33375389f169cd32